<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">suspects</ENAMEX> of producing <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">illicit chemicals</ENAMEX> in another member <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">country</ENAMEX>. This means
