<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">espionage</ENAMEX>, stealing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">company</ENAMEX> secrets for <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">firms</ENAMEX> in their homelands.

